<string>Find The SML Characters!</string>
<key>PayloadDescription</key>
<string>Explore, search, and collect your favorite SML characters in this 2D hidden-character adventure inspired by Find the Markers on Roblox.

Built entirely in Scratch, this 2D game challenges you to explore different areas, look carefully, and discover every hidden character. Can you find them all? 👀

Features
Classic 2D hidden-object gameplay

Explore colorful, detailed maps

Find and collect hidden SML characters

Multiple display modes:

Preserve aspect ratio

1:1 mode

Fullscreen

Available on:

🪟 Windows

🍎 macOS

🐧 Linux

How to Play
Move around the 2D map

Click on hidden characters to collect them

Try to find every single one

Explore carefully — some are very well hidden 👀</string>
